aces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地片入面係講華氏架嘛..."},{"pid":"4640ac44d2454d8fc771e6bfb343262b6da8bd1c","tid":450579,"uid":68728,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T19:14:06.000Z","msg":"溫泉唔流動<br />\n<br />\n河流流動 <br />\n<br />\n呢個係分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee28c8b41ee4abf03b35f9d702d364fcc0995df5","tid":450579,"uid":4190,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T19:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171028/20197351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F20197351&d=KCsqmQiBR0D6uDrfmw%2Fqxh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=7b4ab53c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F20197351&h=59605040\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171028/20197351</a> <br />\n<br />\n秘魯神秘「滾水河」<br />\n生物跌落監生淥熟<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳說秘魯有條河水溫度高達100&deg;C，墮進去的生物都會被活活煮熟。地球物理學家魯佐（Andr&eacute;s Ruzo）尋尋覓覓，終於被他證實傳說原來是真的。<br />\n<br />\n這條河名字叫「Shanay-timpishka」，在土語中解作「用太陽熱力煮沸」之意。魯佐最先從祖父口中聽過這條河的故事，12年後一次家庭聚餐，魯佐得悉嬸嬸曾到訪這條河流，於是在2011年由她帶領下走入森林，終於發現長約6.4公里、最闊處達25米、最深處達6米的熱河。河流雖然遠離任何活火山，但地球的熱水透過裂縫及斷層流出，形成這條河流。<br />\n<br />\n魯佐為YouTube頻道「Great Big Story」拍攝短片，短片在周一上傳。魯佐帶大家探索河流，說可感受到河流散發出的熱力，令人鼻腔及肺內有被焚燒之感。<br />\n<br />\n「我量度過最高溫度是100&deg;C。<span style=\"color: red;\">用日常生活打個比喻，正常咖啡約55&deg;C&hellip;&hellip;你把手放進去，幾秒內就會二級或三級程度燒傷。</span>」魯佐續道：「我見過好些動物掉進去，由雀鳥到爬蟲類都有。像我們這類複雜的有機體，在高溫中情況不妙，會被活生生煮熟。」<br />\n<br />\n河流周圍的森林因伐木而受到破壞，假如不採取行動，此處或完全消失。魯佐正嘗試挽救這片自然奇蹟。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》</blockquote><br />\n紅字1999 中學生都唔會咁樣寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚on9 我都睇到屌哂嘴<br />\n100度咪即個滾囉 比乜撚嘢喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下低又係 講乜撚嘢有機體 100度係嘢都死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n海底有蝦450度都生存緊"},{"pid":"a510c74c9515fab1ac9b2293165af90e33c00bbe","tid":450579,"uid":31887,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T19:43:17.000Z","msg":"好想倒好立克粉"},{"pid":"a488b1eeac2bc7b9e96423c0ab1ed9f077fcd674","tid":450579,"uid":146924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T19:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溫泉唔流動<br />\n<br />\n河流流動 <br />\n<br />\n呢個係分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n溫泉係地下自然湧出來嘅泉水(from wiki)<br />\n呢個係成條河流嘅水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83caae7c86620499d557348d6edb752edf05604d","tid":450579,"uid":146924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T19:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D 熱係邊度黎?</blockquote><br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9e819546c44a83c5174afbaac271f794339fd2","tid":450579,"uid":13250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T19:48:31.000Z","msg":"咁d水咪好乾淨,攤凍佢就飲得唔洗煲"},{"pid":"3c423f0b5c52a4b3bf6777fb2e787889c9f9f865","tid":450579,"uid":26113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T19:54:09.000Z","msg":"上遊放餸 下遊夾餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7380f6ef7f6453e8f98faf7853adb099d8b6de28","tid":450579,"uid":37414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T20:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁d水咪好乾淨,攤凍佢就飲得唔洗煲</blockquote><br />\n咪一樣有d撚樣係到屙尿"},{"pid":"537140cb72fa2513fe107624702644490b29ce23","tid":450579,"uid":12557,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T21:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171028/20197351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F20197351&d=KCsqmQiBR0D6uDrfmw%2Fqxh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=7b4ab53c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F20197351&h=59605040\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171028/20197351</a> <br />\n<br />\n秘魯神秘「滾水河」<br />\n生物跌落監生淥熟<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳說秘魯有條河水溫度高達100&deg;C，墮進去的生物都會被活活煮熟。地球物理學家魯佐（Andr&eacute;s Ruzo）尋尋覓覓，終於被他證實傳說原來是真的。<br />\n<br />\n這條河名字叫「Shanay-timpishka」，在土語中解作「用太陽熱力煮沸」之意。魯佐最先從祖父口中聽過這條河的故事，12年後一次家庭聚餐，魯佐得悉嬸嬸曾到訪這條河流，於是在2011年由她帶領下走入森林，終於發現長約6.4公里、最闊處達25米、最深處達6米的熱河。河流雖然遠離任何活火山，但地球的熱水透過裂縫及斷層流出，形成這條河流。<br />\n<br />\n魯佐為YouTube頻道「Great Big Story」拍攝短片，短片在周一上傳。魯佐帶大家探索河流，說可感受到河流散發出的熱力，令人鼻腔及肺內有被焚燒之感。<br />\n<br />\n「我量度過最高溫度是100&deg;C。<span style=\"color: red;\">用日常生活打個比喻，正常咖啡約55&deg;C&hellip;&hellip;你把手放進去，幾秒內就會二級或三級程度燒傷。</span>」魯佐續道：「我見過好些動物掉進去，由雀鳥到爬蟲類都有。像我們這類複雜的有機體，在高溫中情況不妙，會被活生生煮熟。」<br />\n<br />\n河流周圍的森林因伐木而受到破壞，假如不採取行動，此處或完全消失。魯佐正嘗試挽救這片自然奇蹟。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》</blockquote><br />\n紅字1999 中學生都唔會咁樣寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚on9 我都睇到屌哂嘴<br />\n100度咪即個滾囉 比乜撚嘢喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下低又係 講乜撚嘢有機體 100度係嘢都死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又一個井底蛙衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多年前已經發現左有唔少生物可以生存係過百度溫度<br />\n早幾年係海底火山更加發現左唔少嗜熱非細菌類生物"},{"pid":"42745e0c6ce7e0d2c0f6b7ce747df3b697736a33","tid":450579,"uid":15094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T21:14:01.000Z","msg":"有冇潛水裝備可以扺擋100度入去玩下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461392d84b9361142ff3682d1a39e7725433d35a","tid":450579,"uid":146924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T21:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁d水咪好乾淨,攤凍佢就飲得唔洗煲</blockquote><br />\n邊個同你講啲水煲過就等於乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪一樣有好多雜質喺入面"},{"pid":"f95b9538050ea0469712c6be7d4c231f8ef8e2dc","tid":450579,"uid":112784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T21:26:28.000Z","msg":"美食獵人：世紀湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744be822d745300fed224a9783aab743748d2b83","tid":450579,"uid":10454,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T00:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D 熱係邊度黎?</blockquote><br />\n光+熱=火<br />\n所以<br />\n火-光=熱<br />\n<br />\nD河水其實係失去左光既火黎"},{"pid":"3cbdc6b980bd79c1e78d1f1d862d49e5a07087eb","tid":450579,"uid":72187,"like":26,"dislike":5,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T00:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockq